# Cloudflare Pages redirects — https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# Canonical host is the getsetcraft.com apex. Everything else 301s to it:
# the www variant, and both the apex and www of the .net brand-protection domain.
# All four hostnames must be added as custom domains on the Pages project for
# these host-matched rules to fire.
https://www.getsetcraft.com/*  https://getsetcraft.com/:splat  301
https://getsetcraft.net/*      https://getsetcraft.com/:splat  301
https://www.getsetcraft.net/*  https://getsetcraft.com/:splat  301

# Single source of truth for the app download. The "Download Free" buttons all
# point at /download; this forwards to the signed DMG hosted as a GitHub Release
# asset on the public setcraft-website repo. The /latest/ path is stable: ship a
# new release with an asset named Setcraft.dmg and this URL follows it
# automatically, no edit here needed.
/download  https://github.com/brianhaggis/setcraft-website/releases/latest/download/Setcraft.dmg  302
